(92, 1, '2013-10-10 09:20:51', '2013-10-10 07:20:51', 'OIM prides itself in its ability to deliver results and has a strong commitment to service delivery. As such, we place a high premium on the quality of our consultants and team members.\r\n\r\nWe offer career opportunities for people with proven experience and relevant academic qualifications in the areas of:\r\n\r\nOrganisational performance improvement\r\nHuman resources / employee relations / organisational development / learning & development\r\nOperations management\r\nLeadership development and talent management\r\nIf you fit this bill and have a willingness to travel quite extensively you are welcome to contact us! Also keep an eye on our LinkedIN page where we post most of our vacancies.\r\n\r\nFor more information, or to submit your CV, please mail Suzanne van Zyl at svanzyl@oimgroup.com or call her on +27 21 913 8814/5.', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-10 09:20:51', '2013-10-10 07:20:51', '', 15, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/oim/htdocs/uncategorized/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(93, 1, '2013-10-10 09:22:30', '2013-10-10 07:22:30', 'OIM prides itself in its ability to deliver results and has a strong commitment to service delivery. As such, we place a high premium on the quality of our consultants and team members.\r\n\r\nWe offer career opportunities for people with proven experience and relevant academic qualifications in the areas of:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Organisational performance improvement</li>\r\n	<li>Human resources / employee relations / organisational development / learning &amp; development</li>\r\n	<li>Operations management</li>\r\n	<li>Leadership development and talent management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you fit this bill and have a willingness to travel quite extensively you are welcome to contact us! Also keep an eye on our <a href="http://za.linkedin.com/company/oim-international-pty-ltd?trk=ppro_cprof" target="_blank">LinkedIN page</a> where we post most of our vacancies.\r\n\r\nFor more information, or to submit your CV, please mail Suzanne van Zyl at <a href="mailto:svanzyl@oimgroup.com">svanzyl@oimgroup.com</a> or call her on +27 21 913 8814/5.', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-10 09:22:30', '2013-10-10 07:22:30', '', 15, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/oim/htdocs/uncategorized/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(94, 1, '2013-10-10 10:38:31', '2013-10-10 08:38:31', '<img class="size-full wp-image-95 alignnone" alt="Umbono Mining Solutions" src="http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/oim/htdocs/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/umbono.gif" width="164" height="44" />\r\n\r\nOIM Umbono Mining Solutions is a joint venture between OIM and Umbono Capital, combining the unique skills and experience of the two companies to unlock operational efficiency in the mining industry.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.oimumbono.com/" target="_blank">www.oimumbono.com</a> and <a href="http://www.umbono.com/" target="_blank">www.umbono.com</a> for more information.', 'OIM UMBONO Mining Solutions', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oim-umbono-mining-solutions', '', '', '2013-10-10 11:13:08', '2013-10-10 09:13:08', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/oim/htdocs/?post_type=clients&#038;p=94', 0, 'clients', '', 0),
